# AAVE_BORROWED_TOKEN_ADDRESS=0xa0b86a33e6441b8c4b8b8c4b8b8c4b8b8c4b8b8c
# AAVE_SUPPLY_TOKEN_DECIMALS=18
# AAVE_BORROWED_TOKEN_DECIMALS=6

# ========================================
# NOTES
# ========================================
# 1. Make sure to replace all placeholder values with your actual data
# 2. Keep your API keys secure and never commit them to version control
# 3. Test with small amounts first
# 4. Monitor the bot's output to ensure it's working correctly
# 5. The bot will print its configuration on startup for verification 